# ==========================================
# MiMatcha - Environment Variables
# ==========================================
#
# Cara deploy ke Railway:
#   1. Push repo ke GitHub
#   2. Di Railway Dashboard → New Project → Deploy from GitHub repo
#   3. Tambah PostgreSQL addon: New → Database → Add PostgreSQL
#      → Railway auto-inject DATABASE_URL ke app
#   4. Set variabel wajib di Railway Settings → Variables:
#      - OPENROUTER_API_KEY (daftar di https://openrouter.ai/keys)
#      - VITE_OPENROUTER_API_KEY (sama dengan di atas)
#   5. Deploy akan otomatis jalan.
#      Database schema auto-terbuat saat pertama kali API dipanggil.
# ==========================================

# === WAJIB: OpenRouter API Key (untuk deteksi uang AI) ===
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=your_openrouter_api_key_here

# === WAJIB: Sama seperti di atas (dibutuhkan frontend) ===
VITE_OPENROUTER_API_KEY=your_openrouter_api_key_here

# === OTOMATIS dari Railway PostgreSQL addon ===
# DATABASE_URL akan diisi otomatis. Tidak perlu setting manual.
